            &lt;/a&gt;
          &lt;/figure&gt;
                &lt;figcaption class=&quot;has-text-centered is-italic is-size-6&quot;&gt;Careful planning pt. 2.&lt;/figcaption&gt;
              &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
